description:
Full recipe on: http://www.astigvegan.com/vegan-banana-bread-tablea-kasuy-flavor/

Heres a vegan banana bread recipe with Filipino flavors -tablea dark chocolate and kasuy/cashews! Super easy to make and very beginner-friendly. I finally got an oven so the first order of business is this easy vegan banana bread, inspired by the recipe of @chefchloe. It has become my go-to easy bake since the beginning of pandemic. I dont think Ill ever get off this banana bread trend especially now that Im in the country with the best bananas in the world ! Kain na, lets eat!

#kaivegan #filipinovegan #veganfilipino #fellowastigvegan #astigvegan #vegan  #easybaking
